b'This picture is called "Don\'t Hog the Bathroom". The print unframed measures 12x16 inches. The frame will add about one more inch per side. This print is so cute! They are obviously preparing for a bubble bath since there are bubbles floating through the air.  There is a towel hanging over the edge of the bathtub.  The background is textured white. Across the front of the tub are the words "don\'t hog the Bathroom". Choose your lath frame color to customize your product. b'This picture is called "Meet Again Someday". The print unframed measures 12x16 inches. The frame will add about one more inch per side.  This print has an old fashioned small white church in the country with trees and farming scenery in the background.  The saying on the print reads "If you could see me now, you wouldn\'t shed a tear. Though you may not understand why I\'m no longer here. Remember my spirit, that\'s the real me. I\'m still very much alive, oh if you could only see! I\'ve beheld our Father\'s face. I\'ve touched my Saviour\'s hand. The angels all rejoiced as I entered the Promised Land. Beyond the gates of pearl, I walk on golden streets. I\'ve touched the walls of jasper dipped my foot in the crystal sea. The beauty is beyond words, nothing can compare. I\'ve even seen your mansion; someday I will meet you there. Allow Jesus to be your guide, His word will show you the way. So, please, don\'t cry! We will meet again someday!" Such a touching saying to comfort anyone who is grieving the loss of someone close to them or to have in remembrance of someone they love.  Beautiful print with multiple frame selections to choose from.  Choose your lath frame color to customize your product. All frames have a vintage wire along the top of the frame for quick and easy wall hanging.'
